spec_data.Name: atlas-corei2-static
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the ATLAS (Automatically Tuned Linear Algebra
Software) static libraries compiled with optimizations for the Corei2 (Ivy/Sandy bridge)
CPUs. The base ATLAS builds for the x86_64 architecture are made for the hammer64 CPUs.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 17 Aug 2017 10:43:53 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: ATLAS libraries for Corei2 (Ivy/Sandy bridge) CPUs
